{"parentUuid":"218d850e-be57-49a6-9afb-31c2f67a7666","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a4e4c9b00c5efe637","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CcvuVNVZjULhzokgAMSzF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01KKcWfWiK1v4uNoqdNZXmkL","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/plan.md","offset":196,"limit":14},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3424,"cache_read_input_tokens":120138,"output_tokens":1355,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3424},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1355,"cache_read_input_tokens":120138,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3424,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3424,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcvuVLVm8Yh4EXSmAgdpx","attributionAgent":"planning","type":"assistant","uuid":"0d8d7e71-a8b2-4db9-996d-e2365b93829d","timestamp":"2026-07-11T20:32:12.633Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
{"parentUuid":"0d8d7e71-a8b2-4db9-996d-e2365b93829d","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"65871126-fcc0-41d2-a9f9-a85b1fd15ac2","agentId":"a4e4c9b00c5efe637","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KKcWfWiK1v4uNoqdNZXmkL","type":"tool_result","content":"196\t`00:00Z` of D+1 (not counted).\n197\t\n198\t### Response shape\n199\t\n200\t`DailyUsageResponse(extra=\"forbid\")`: `{ \"date\": \"<echoed YYYY-MM-DD>\", \"metrics\":\n201\t[ { \"metric\": str, \"event_count\": int }, … ] }`, metrics ordered by `metric`. Empty day\n202\t→ `metrics: []` with 200 (never 404) — same \"absence is a valid answer, not an error\"\n203\tcontract `get_usage` documents (`extra=\"forbid\"` on both models is the ASVS 15.3.1\n204\tminimal-projection posture; `api_key_id` is never echoed back).\n205\t\n206\t## Auth\n207\t\n208\tReuses the existing API-key facade unchanged: `require_api_key`\n209\t(`src/auth/__init__.py`) parses the split-token `Authorization: Bearer"}]},"uuid":"563e10e2-a466-4efb-8aee-e90f172ce30e","timestamp":"2026-07-11T20:32:12.692Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/plan.md","content":"`00:00Z` of D+1 (not counted).\n\n### Response shape\n\n`DailyUsageResponse(extra=\"forbid\")`: `{ \"date\": \"<echoed YYYY-MM-DD>\", \"metrics\":\n[ { \"metric\": str, \"event_count\": int }, … ] }`, metrics ordered by `metric`. Empty day\n→ `metrics: []` with 200 (never 404) — same \"absence is a valid answer, not an error\"\ncontract `get_usage` documents (`extra=\"forbid\"` on both models is the ASVS 15.3.1\nminimal-projection posture; `api_key_id` is never echoed back).\n\n## Auth\n\nReuses the existing API-key facade unchanged: `require_api_key`\n(`src/auth/__init__.py`) parses the split-token `Authorization: Bearer","numLines":14,"startLine":196,"totalLines":481}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"0d8d7e71-a8b2-4db9-996d-e2365b93829d","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
{"parentUuid":"563e10e2-a466-4efb-8aee-e90f172ce30e","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a4e4c9b00c5efe637","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CcvuX22Zwc8hvT5Yab1wa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EhUsCgVUtiTJG6ddsadkYW","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/.pipeline/plan.md","old_string":"## Auth\n\nReuses the existing API-key facade unchanged: `require_api_key`","new_string":"## Stack notes\n\nThis is an existing project with an established, `CLAUDE.md`-recorded stack; this feature\nintroduces **no stack change and no new dependency**, so every default is endorsed as-is:\n\n- **Language/framework: Python 3.12 + FastAPI** — kept; the endpoint is a standard FastAPI\n  route reusing the existing router/dependency/schema patterns.\n- **Data store: PostgreSQL** — kept; reads the existing `usage_rollup` table via the\n  existing async SQLAlchemy session + RLS machinery. No new table, no migration\n  (Alembic untouched).\n- **Auth: API keys (Argon2id, split-token), customer-scoped** — kept; reuses\n  `require_api_key` verbatim, no third-party IdP, no scope change.\n- **Observability: structlog → CloudWatch/X-Ray + Sentry** — kept; one new structured\n  `usage.daily.read` event through the existing logger facade.\n- **Rate limiting: Redis token bucket (Tier-1 IP / Tier-2 per-key)** — kept; reused via\n  the existing dependency + middleware.\n\n**One conscious contract deviation** (flagged for the checkpoint, not a stack change): this\nendpoint returns **HTTP 400** for a malformed/missing `date`, whereas the codebase's\nPydantic query models otherwise surface validation failures as 422. The brief pins 400;\nthe split (400 for the date *value*, 422 for *undeclared params*) is detailed in\n*Backend → the 400-not-422 decision*.\n\n## Auth\n\nReuses the existing API-key facade unchanged: `require_api_key`"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1660,"cache_read_input_tokens":123562,"output_tokens":725,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1660},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":725,"cache_read_input_tokens":123562,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1660,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1660,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcvuWxBdmmcLaqWHDDXQJ","attributionAgent":"planning","type":"assistant","uuid":"cd03c515-28d6-4440-8702-67b4611c9e5a","timestamp":"2026-07-11T20:32:30.562Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
